  "title": "COOK",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>This Korean Restaurant seeks an Assistant Cook with at least 5 years of kitchen experience to prepare Korean side dishes, maintain strict hygiene, and manage kitchen materials to ensure freshness and sufficiency.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare Korean side dishes following authentic recipes to maintain quality and consistency</li><li>Apply strict hygiene practices to ensure a clean and safe kitchen environment</li><li>Monitor and maintain sufficient and fresh kitchen materials to support daily cooking operations</li><li>Collaborate with kitchen team members to support smooth food preparation and service</li></ul><p><strong>Required competencies and certifications</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of kitchen-related experiences.</li></ul>",
